Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:58.25,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}泣きそうな 青リンゴ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:58.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}青蘋果兒 雙眼哭紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:02.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}抱えてる　胸の奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:02.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}唯有夢想 緊抱胸中
