Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}無數跌倒 倔強挺胸（儘管已千瘡百孔）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:10.15,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}窮屈な　空睨む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:10.15,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}不屑瞪著 呆滯天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:17.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}運命に　従順に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:17.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}命運匆匆 吾等不從
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:24.64,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}熟すのを待つもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:24.64,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}乾等一生 吾心不容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:30.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}千の風　あがいて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:30.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}風吹雨打 屹立不動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:34.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}吹け吹け　叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:34.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}可那風兒 越吼越凶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}わたしは　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}但我依然 夢想在胸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:42.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}しゃぼん玉　信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:42.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}肥皂泡中 定有彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:46.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}予期せぬ　上昇して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:46.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}偶爾得志 騰雲行空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}嵐に　下降して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}偶爾迷失 風暴之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:54.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}あらがう　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:54.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}抗爭不止 信念不鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:58.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}しゃぼん玉　生きてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:58.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}肥皂泡兒 亦能騰空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:05.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}弾ける瞬間　虹、放て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:05.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}破裂瞬間 釋放彩虹

